Sentencas: High performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells requires improvements especially in the microstructure of the cathode layer.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: New cobalt-free cathode materials are used because cobalt-containing cathodes have higher thermal expansion coefficients, poor long-term chemical stability, and lower mechanical stability.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: Recently cobalt-free cathodes have been proposed to solve these issues by using deposition methods other than electrospray deposition (ESD).
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: In this study, ESD method is used to develop a cobalt-free cathode layer.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: The electrolyte layer is gadolinium-doped ceria that is deposited with La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7 Cr0.3O3-delta (LSFCr) prepared by 2-butoxyethanol and ethylene glycol solvents as opposed to conventional solvents.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: Experimental ESD parameters are tested at different levels and combinations by applying statistical experimental design methods to optimize the microstructure.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC

Sentencas: Coating deposited as such demonstrated higher electrochemical performance than similar electrodes fabricated by other methods.
Titulo: Effects of electrospraying parameters on deposition of La0.3Sr0.7Fe0.7Cr0.3O3-δ cathode layer on GDC
